               <msContents>
                  <summary>Amharic Commentary on Our Father, የአቡነ፡ ዘበሰማያት፡ ትርጓሜ፡, Notes on orders of the rite of baptism and the Mass, in Amharic</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                    <locus from="1r" to="41v" facs="002"/>
                     <textLang mainLang="am" otherLangs="gez">Amharic and Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                     <title type="complete" ref="LIT5934CommOurFather"/>
                     <incipit xml:lang="am">
                       በስመ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ ወመንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ፩አምላክ፡ ብሎ፡ መጽሐፍ፡ እንዲጀምር፡ ጌታችን፡ እግዚእነ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ አንትሙሰ፡ ሶበ፡ ትጸልዩ፡ ከመዝ፡ በሉ፡ አለ፡
                     </incipit>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                    <locus from="41v" to="42v" facs="043"/>
                    <title>Notes on orders of the rite of baptism and the Mass, in Amharic</title>
                    <textLang mainLang="am" otherLangs="gez"/>
                    <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                      እጽሕፍ፡ ሥርዓተ፡ ቤተ፡ ክርስቲያን፡ ቀዳሽ፡ ቢታጣ፡ ጥምቀት፡<gap reason="omitted"/>
                    </incipit>
                  </msItem>
